text: Kirchham (literally "Churcham") is a municipality in Passau in Bavaria in Germany. Kirchham has 27 subdivisions: * Angloh * Bach * Ed * Eggen * Erlbach * Hinterberg * Hinteröd * Hof * Hofgarten * Hoheneich * Kirchham * Moos * Ort * Osterholzen * Reisner * Reith * Roidenhub * Schambach * Senget * Stadlöd * Staubermühle * Stocking * Tutting * Uttelsberg * Waldstadt * Weinberg * Zanklöd Kirchham is twinned with Churcham, England. ==References== Category:Passau (district)
title: Kirchham
